    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse your <strong>chickpeas</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> into quarters</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p>",
