    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 10-15 min, add the <strong>remaining chickpeas</strong> to the tray[s] with the veg, sprinkle over your <strong>ground cumin</strong>,<strong> </strong>then<strong> </strong>drizzle with 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and give it a good mix up</p><p>Add your<strong> Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the tray[s], drizzle with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span><strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a further 10-15 min or until everything is cooked through and golden</p>",
