    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add a small squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong>, 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]<strong> </span>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> to a small bowl and stir it all together</p><p>Once the veg is cooked, squeeze the <strong>roasted</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> from its skin into the bowl and discard the skin</p><p>Mash the<strong> roasted garlic </strong>with a fork and whisk it into the dressing – this is your<strong> roasted garlic dressing</strong></p>",
