    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> beetroot hummus</strong> with the<strong> bulgur wheat</strong>,<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>roasted veg </strong>to the side</p><p>Drizzle the<strong> roasted garlic dressing</strong> all over and garnish with the <strong>remaining lemon wedges</strong></p><p>Garnish with your <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
